IVL ArabCeleb Dataset 

ArabCeleb contains over 1930 utterances for 100 celebrities, extracted from videos uploaded to YouTube.  

We provide Youtube URLs, associated gender, and age group, as
well as cropped audio segments from the dataset.
The copyright of both the original and cropped versions
of the videos remains with the original owners.

